 * must also have a value: 
 * CQP_TOTAL_EXPORTS_CIF_PERCENTAGE, CQP_TOTAL_EXPORTS_FOB_PERCENTAGE, or CQP_TOTAL_EXPORTS_OI_PERCENTAGE.
